OL,3,C'The mosque can be rebuilt but the
OL,4,Clives lost cannot', Suothport chairman
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe chairman of a mosque attacked when
OL,8,Fviolent disorder broke out in
OL,9,FSouthport says "it can be rebuilt but
OL,10,Fthe lives lost cannot".
OL,12,FIbrahim Hussein was inside Southport
OL,13,FMosque on Tuesday 30 July when far-
OL,14,Fright demonstrators surrounded the
OL,15,Fplace of worship.
OL,17,FProtesters shouted abuse at the people
OL,18,Finside while throwing stones and
OL,19,Fbricks at the building.
