OL,3,C'The mosque can be rebuilt but the
OL,4,Clives lost cannot', Suothport chairman
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FMr Hussein said the focus now is on
OL,8,Fthe families of the victims and not
OL,9,Fthe people who caused disruption the
OL,10,Fday after mass stabbings took place.
OL,12,FHe said: "They can destroy this place
OL,13,Fand we can rebuild it, but the lives
OL,14,Fthat have been lost, we can't ever
OL,15,Fbring them back so all our focus
OL,16,Fshould be with the families."
OL,18,FMore than 50 police officers were
OL,19,Finjured due to the violence, with 27
OL,20,Fofficers taken to hospital, according
OL,21,Fto North West Ambulance Service.
