OL,12,FNine-year-old Alice Dasilva Aguiar,
OL,13,Fsix-year-old Bebe King and seven-year-
OL,14,Fold Elsie Dot Stancombe died after
OL,15,Fsustaining serious injuries when a
OL,16,Fknifeman entered the Hart Centre
OL,17,Fduring a Taylor Swift-themed dance
OL,18,Fclass Monday 29 July.
